flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> OpenUI[Open Bank Account Setup Web Interface]
    OpenUI --> EnterFields[Enter bank_name, account_holder, iban, bic, account_type, currency]
    EnterFields --> Encrypt[Apply end-to-end encryption]
    Encrypt --> Tokenize[Tokenize sensitive data]
    Tokenize --> PCI[Ensure PCI DSS compliance]
    PCI --> IbanCheck{IBAN format valid?}
    IbanCheck -- No --> IbanError[Show IBAN format error]
    IbanError --> EnterFields
    IbanCheck -- Yes --> BicCheck{BIC exists?}
    BicCheck -- No --> BicError[Show BIC not found error]
    BicError --> EnterFields
    BicCheck -- Yes --> DupCheck{Duplicate account?}
    DupCheck -- Yes --> DupError[Show duplicate prevention error]
    DupError --> EnterFields
    DupCheck -- No --> Save[Save bank account setup]
    Save --> End([End])